description:
Dermatologist and self-proclaimed fat expert Dr. Paul Jarrod Frank shares all the new ways people are getting rid of fat and cellulite—without dieting. Plus, everything you ever wanted to know about natural oils, why makeup tutorials trigger ASMR (euphoric tingles), and deep thoughts on the mom haircut.
